Chapter 1: Basic Concepts

1.1 基本定义与记号

生存时间和基本函数

# 示例：生成模拟数据展示基本函数关系
t <- seq(0, 10, 0.1)
lambda <- 0.5  # 指数分布参数

# 四个基本函数
h_t <- lambda  # 恒定hazard
H_t <- lambda * t  # 累积hazard
S_t <- exp(-lambda * t)  # 生存函数
f_t <- lambda * exp(-lambda * t)  # 密度函数
F_t <- 1 - S_t  # 累积分布函数

# 可视化
par(mfrow = c(2, 2))
plot(t, S_t, type = "l", lwd = 2, col = "blue",
     main = "生存函数 S(t)", ylab = "S(t)", xlab = "Time")
plot(t, h_t * rep(1, length(t)), type = "l", lwd = 2, col = "red",
     main = "风险函数 h(t) - 恒定", ylab = "h(t)", xlab = "Time")
plot(t, H_t, type = "l", lwd = 2, col = "green",
     main = "累积风险 H(t)", ylab = "H(t)", xlab = "Time")
plot(t, f_t, type = "l", lwd = 2, col = "purple",
     main = "密度函数 f(t)", ylab = "f(t)", xlab = "Time")

par(mfrow = c(1, 1))

关键关系式：

  • \(h(t) = \frac{f(t)}{S(t)} = -\frac{d\log S(t)}{dt}\)
  • \(S(t) = \exp(-H(t)) = \exp\left(-\int_0^t h(u)du\right)\)
  • \(H(t) = -\log S(t)\)
  • \(f(t) = h(t)S(t)\)

条件概率计算

# 示例：指数分布的条件概率
# 已知存活到时间s，再存活到s+t的概率

lambda <- 0.3
s <- 2
t <- 3

# P(T > s+t | T > s) = S(s+t) / S(s)
S_s <- exp(-lambda * s)
S_st <- exp(-lambda * (s + t))
cond_prob <- S_st / S_s

cat("P(T >", s+t, "| T >", s, ") =", cond_prob, "\n")
## P(T > 5 | T > 2 ) = 0.4065697
cat("直接计算 exp(-lambda*t) =", exp(-lambda * t), "\n")
## 直接计算 exp(-lambda*t) = 0.4065697
cat("验证无记忆性质（指数分布）\n")
## 验证无记忆性质（指数分布）

1.2 删失类型

右删失示例

# 模拟右删失数据
set.seed(123)
n <- 100

# 真实事件时间（指数分布）
true_time <- rexp(n, rate = 0.2)

# 删失时间（均匀分布）
censor_time <- runif(n, 0, 15)

# 观测时间和删失指示
obs_time <- pmin(true_time, censor_time)
event <- as.numeric(true_time <= censor_time)

cat("样本量:", n, "\n")
## 样本量: 100
cat("事件数:", sum(event), "\n")
## 事件数: 73
cat("删失数:", sum(1 - event), "\n")
## 删失数: 27
cat("删失率:", round(mean(1 - event) * 100, 1), "%\n")
## 删失率: 27 %
# 创建生存对象
surv_obj <- Surv(time = obs_time, event = event)
head(data.frame(obs_time, event, surv_obj), 10)

左截断（延迟进入）示例

# 示例：研究从1990年开始，但只观察1985年后出生且存活到1990年的个体
set.seed(456)
n <- 50

# 出生时间（1985-1990之间）
birth_year <- runif(n, 1985, 1990)

# 进入研究时间（1990年）
entry_year <- 1990

# 事件时间（从出生算起）
event_year <- birth_year + rexp(n, rate = 0.1)

# 删失时间（研究结束于2000年）
censor_year <- 2000

# 只观察存活到1990年的个体
entry_time <- entry_year - birth_year  # 左截断时间
obs_time <- pmin(event_year, censor_year) - birth_year
event <- as.numeric(event_year < censor_year)

# 左截断数据
left_trunc_data <- data.frame(
  entry = entry_time,
  exit = obs_time,
  event = event
)

Chapter 2: Kaplan-Meier 估计

2.1 KM估计量的计算

手工计算示例

# 示例数据：2, 3+, 5, 8, 8+  (+ 表示删失)
time <- c(2, 3, 5, 8, 8)
event <- c(1, 0, 1, 1, 0)

# 创建KM表格
km_table <- data.frame(
  t = c(0, 2, 3, 5, 8),
  n_risk = c(5, 5, 4, 3, 2),
  n_event = c(0, 1, 0, 1, 1),
  n_censor = c(0, 0, 1, 0, 1),
  survival = c(1, 0.8, 0.8, 0.533, 0.267)
)

km_table$hazard <- km_table$n_event / km_table$n_risk
km_table$se_component <- ifelse(km_table$n_event > 0,
                                 km_table$n_event / (km_table$n_risk * (km_table$n_risk - km_table$n_event)),
                                 0)

print(km_table)
##   t n_risk n_event n_censor survival    hazard se_component
## 1 0      5       0        0    1.000 0.0000000    0.0000000
## 2 2      5       1        0    0.800 0.2000000    0.0500000
## 3 3      4       0        1    0.800 0.0000000    0.0000000
## 4 5      3       1        0    0.533 0.3333333    0.1666667
## 5 8      2       1        1    0.267 0.5000000    0.5000000
# 计算Greenwood标准误（在t=8时）
greenwood_sum <- sum(km_table$se_component[km_table$t <= 8 & km_table$n_event > 0])
se_s8 <- km_table$survival[km_table$t == 8] * sqrt(greenwood_sum)

cat("\nGreenwood方差成分之和:", greenwood_sum, "\n")
## 
## Greenwood方差成分之和: 0.7166667
cat("SE(S(8)):", se_s8, "\n")
## SE(S(8)): 0.226032

使用R的survival包

# 使用survival包计算
km_fit <- survfit(Surv(time, event) ~ 1)

# 查看详细结果
summary(km_fit)
## Call: survfit(formula = Surv(time, event) ~ 1)
## 
##  time n.risk n.event survival std.err lower 95% CI upper 95% CI

##     5      3       1    0.533   0.248       0.2142            1

# 绘制KM曲线
plot(km_fit, conf.int = TRUE,
     xlab = "Time", ylab = "Survival Probability",
     main = "Kaplan-Meier Survival Curve",
     col = c("blue", "red", "red"),

       col = c("blue", "red"), lwd = 2)

2.2 置信区间

三种置信区间方法

# 使用lung数据集
data(lung)
lung_clean <- lung %>% filter(!is.na(sex))

# 计算不同类型的置信区间
km_plain <- survfit(Surv(time, status - 1) ~ 1, data = lung_clean, conf.type = "plain")
km_log <- survfit(Surv(time, status - 1) ~ 1, data = lung_clean, conf.type = "log")
km_loglog <- survfit(Surv(time, status - 1) ~ 1, data = lung_clean, conf.type = "log-log")

# 比较在特定时间点的CI
time_point <- 365

# 提取在该时间点的估计
summary(km_plain, times = time_point)$surv
## [1] 0.4092416
summary(km_log, times = time_point)$surv
## [1] 0.4092416
summary(km_loglog, times = time_point)$surv
## [1] 0.4092416
# 可视化比较
par(mfrow = c(1, 3))
plot(km_plain, conf.int = TRUE, main = "Plain CI",
     xlab = "Days", ylab = "Survival", xlim = c(0, 1000))
plot(km_log, conf.int = TRUE, main = "Log CI",
     xlab = "Days", ylab = "Survival", xlim = c(0, 1000))
plot(km_loglog, conf.int = TRUE, main = "Log-Log CI", # Default method
     xlab = "Days", ylab = "Survival", xlim = c(0, 1000))

par(mfrow = c(1, 1))

2.3 Backward Calculation（反推计算）

从S(t)反推d_i和r_i

# 示例：给定S(t)和样本量，反推事件数和风险集大小
n <- 21
survival_estimates <- c(1.000, 0.905, 0.762, 0.667, 0.571)
time_points <- c(0, 2, 5, 7, 10)

# 创建表格
backward_table <- data.frame(
  time = time_points,
  S_t = survival_estimates,
  S_prev = c(NA, survival_estimates[-length(survival_estimates)])
)

# 计算d_i/r_i
backward_table$d_over_r <- with(backward_table,
                                 ifelse(!is.na(S_prev), 1 - S_t/S_prev, NA))

# 假设从r_1 = n开始
backward_table$r_i <- c(21, 21, 18, 16, 14)
backward_table$d_i <- round(backward_table$d_over_r * backward_table$r_i)
backward_table$c_i <- c(0, 0, 2, 1, NA)  # 删失数

print(backward_table)
##   time   S_t S_prev  d_over_r r_i d_i c_i
## 1    0 1.000     NA        NA  21  NA   0
## 2    2 0.905  1.000 0.0950000  21   2   0
## 3    5 0.762  0.905 0.1580110  18   3   2
## 4    7 0.667  0.762 0.1246719  16   2   1
## 5   10 0.571  0.667 0.1439280  14   2  NA
# 验证
cat("\n验证:\n")
## 
## 验证:
cat("总事件数:", sum(backward_table$d_i, na.rm = TRUE), "\n")
## 总事件数: 9
cat("总删失数:", sum(backward_table$c_i, na.rm = TRUE), "\n")
## 总删失数: 3
cat("总计:", sum(backward_table$d_i, na.rm = TRUE) + sum(backward_table$c_i, na.rm = TRUE), "\n")
## 总计: 12

Chapter 3: 比较两组生存曲线

3.1 Logrank检验

手工计算示例

# 示例数据：两组的生存时间
group1_time <- c(6, 7, 10, 15, 19, 25)
group1_event <- c(1, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0)

group2_time <- c(1, 1, 2, 2, 3, 4, 4, 8, 17, 23)
group2_event <- c(1, 1, 1, 1, 1, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0)

# 合并数据
surv_data <- data.frame(
  time = c(group1_time, group2_time),
  event = c(group1_event, group2_event),
  group = c(rep("Group 1", length(group1_time)),
            rep("Group 2", length(group2_time)))
)

# 使用survival包进行logrank检验
logrank_test <- survdiff(Surv(time, event) ~ group, data = surv_data)
print(logrank_test)
## Call:
## survdiff(formula = Surv(time, event) ~ group, data = surv_data)
## 
##                N Observed Expected (O-E)^2/E (O-E)^2/V
## group=Group 1  6        4     5.78     0.549      1.25
## group=Group 2 10        7     5.22     0.609      1.25
## 
##  Chisq= 1.2  on 1 degrees of freedom, p= 0.3
# 手工构建logrank表格（仅显示有事件的时间）
event_times <- sort(unique(surv_data$time[surv_data$event == 1]))

logrank_table <- data.frame(
  time = event_times,
  n1 = sapply(event_times, function(t) sum(surv_data$time >= t & surv_data$group == "Group 1")),
  n2 = sapply(event_times, function(t) sum(surv_data$time >= t & surv_data$group == "Group 2")),
  d1 = sapply(event_times, function(t) sum(surv_data$time == t & surv_data$event == 1 & surv_data$group == "Group 1")),
  d2 = sapply(event_times, function(t) sum(surv_data$time == t & surv_data$event == 1 & surv_data$group == "Group 2"))
)

logrank_table$n_total <- logrank_table$n1 + logrank_table$n2
logrank_table$d_total <- logrank_table$d1 + logrank_table$d2
logrank_table$E1 <- (logrank_table$n1 * logrank_table$d_total) / logrank_table$n_total
logrank_table$V <- with(logrank_table,
                        (n1 * n2 * d_total * (n_total - d_total)) /
                          (n_total^2 * (n_total - 1)))

print(logrank_table)
##   time n1 n2 d1 d2 n_total d_total        E1         V
## 1    1  6 10  0  2      16       2 0.7500000 0.4375000
## 2    2  6  8  0  2      14       2 0.8571429 0.4521193
## 3    3  6  6  0  1      12       1 0.5000000 0.2500000
## 4    4  6  5  0  1      11       1 0.5454545 0.2479339
## 5    6  6  3  1  0       9       1 0.6666667 0.2222222
## 6    7  5  3  1  0       8       1 0.6250000 0.2343750
## 7    8  4  3  0  1       7       1 0.5714286 0.2448980
## 8   10  4  2  1  0       6       1 0.6666667 0.2222222
## 9   15  3  2  1  0       5       1 0.6000000 0.2400000
# 计算检验统计量
O1 <- sum(logrank_table$d1)
E1 <- sum(logrank_table$E1)
V <- sum(logrank_table$V)
chi_sq <- (O1 - E1)^2 / V
p_value <- 1 - pchisq(chi_sq, df = 1)

cat("\nLogrank Test Results:\n")
## 
## Logrank Test Results:
cat("Observed events in Group 1 (O1):", O1, "\n")
## Observed events in Group 1 (O1): 4
cat("Expected events in Group 1 (E1):", E1, "\n")
## Expected events in Group 1 (E1): 5.782359
cat("Variance (V):", V, "\n")
## Variance (V): 2.551271
cat("Chi-square statistic:", chi_sq, "\n")
## Chi-square statistic: 1.245185
cat("P-value:", p_value, "\n")
## P-value: 0.2644741

Cox模型的Partial Likelihood（部分似然）

重要概念：Cox模型使用partial likelihood而不是完整的likelihood。

  • 原因：Cox模型是半参数模型，不对基线风险\(h_0(t)\)做参数假设
  • 方法：通过条件在每个事件时间的风险集上，避免估计\(h_0(t)\)
  • 公式： \[L(\beta) = \prod_{i=1}^D \frac{\exp(\beta^T Z_{(i)})}{\sum_{j \in R(t_{(i)})} \exp(\beta^T Z_j)}\]

其中\(R(t_i)\)是时间\(t_i\)的风险集

  • 优点：
    1. 不需要指定\(h_0(t)\)的参数形式
    2. 仍然可以进行有效推断
    3. 计算相对简单

6.1 指数分布

指数分布的性质

# 拟合指数分布（使用survreg，AFT参数化）
exp_model <- survreg(Surv(time, status - 1) ~ sex + age,
                     data = lung_clean, dist = "exponential")
summary(exp_model)
## 
## Call:
## survreg(formula = Surv(time, status - 1) ~ sex + age, data = lung_clean, 
##     dist = "exponential")
##                Value Std. Error     z      p
## (Intercept)  6.35967    0.63547 10.01 <2e-16
## sex          0.48093    0.16709  2.88  0.004
## age         -0.01562    0.00911 -1.72  0.086
## 
## Scale fixed at 1 
## 
## Exponential distribution
## Loglik(model)= -1156.1   Loglik(intercept only)= -1162.3
##  Chisq= 12.48 on 2 degrees of freedom, p= 0.002 
## Number of Newton-Raphson Iterations: 4 
## n= 228
# 注意：survreg使用AFT参数化
# 转换为PH参数化
# AFT: log(T) = mu + beta*Z + sigma*W
# PH: h(t|Z) = h0(t) * exp(beta_PH * Z)
# 关系: beta_PH = -beta_AFT / sigma

# 对于指数分布，sigma = 1
beta_aft <- coef(exp_model)
beta_ph <- -beta_aft  # 除了截距

cat("\nAFT参数化的系数:\n")
## 
## AFT参数化的系数:
print(beta_aft)
## (Intercept)         sex         age 
##  6.35967154  0.48093492 -0.01561871

## 
## PH参数化的系数（不包括截距）:
print(beta_ph[-1])
##         sex         age 
## -0.48093492  0.01561871
cat("\n风险比 (PH parameterization):\n")
## 
## 风险比 (PH parameterization):
print(exp(beta_ph[-1]))
##       sex       age 
## 0.6182051 1.0157413
# 验证指数假设
cox_model <- coxph(Surv(time, status - 1) ~ sex + age, data = lung_clean)
km_fit <- survfit(cox_model)

# 绘制log(S(t)) vs t
plot(km_fit$time, log(km_fit$surv), type = "l",
     xlab = "Time", ylab = "log(S(t))",
     main = "Check Exponential Assumption: log(S(t)) vs t",
     col = "blue", lwd = 2)
abline(a = 0, b = -0.002, col = "red", lty = 2)  # 参考线

cat("如果近似直线，则支持指数分布假设\n")
## 如果近似直线，则支持指数分布假设

无记忆性质验证

# 指数分布的无记忆性质
# P(T > s+t | T > s) = P(T > t)

lambda <- 0.01  # 假设的hazard rate
s <- 100
t <- 50

# 条件概率
cond_prob <- exp(-lambda * t)

# 直接计算
prob_s <- exp(-lambda * s)
prob_st <- exp(-lambda * (s + t))
cond_prob_direct <- prob_st / prob_s

cat("使用无记忆性质: P(T >", t, "| T >", s, ") =", cond_prob, "\n")
## 使用无记忆性质: P(T > 50 | T > 100 ) = 0.6065307
cat("直接计算: P(T >", s+t, "| T >", s, ") =", cond_prob_direct, "\n")
## 直接计算: P(T > 150 | T > 100 ) = 0.6065307
cat("两者相等，验证无记忆性质\n")
## 两者相等，验证无记忆性质

weibull_model <- survreg(Surv(time, status - 1) ~ sex + age,
                         data = lung_clean, dist = "weibull")
summary(weibull_model)
## 
## Call:
## survreg(formula = Surv(time, status - 1) ~ sex + age, data = lung_clean, 
##     dist = "weibull")
##                Value Std. Error     z       p
## (Intercept)  6.27485    0.48137 13.04 < 2e-16
## sex          0.38209    0.12748  3.00  0.0027
## age         -0.01226    0.00696 -1.76  0.0781
## Log(scale)  -0.28230    0.06188 -4.56 5.1e-06
## 
## Scale= 0.754 
## 
## Weibull distribution
## Loglik(model)= -1147.1   Loglik(intercept only)= -1153.9
##  Chisq= 13.59 on 2 degrees of freedom, p= 0.0011 
## Number of Newton-Raphson Iterations: 5 
## n= 228
# Weibull参数
# h(t) = lambda * alpha * t^(alpha-1)
# S(t) = exp(-lambda * t^alpha)

# 从survreg提取参数
scale <- weibull_model$scale  # 这是1/alpha
alpha <- 1 / scale

cat("\nWeibull形状参数 alpha:", alpha, "\n")
## 
## Weibull形状参数 alpha: 1.32617
if(alpha > 1) {
  cat("alpha > 1: 风险递增\n")
} else if(alpha < 1) {
  cat("alpha < 1: 风险递减\n")
} else {
  cat("alpha = 1: 恒定风险（指数分布）\n")
}
## alpha > 1: 风险递增
# AFT系数
beta_aft_weibull <- coef(weibull_model)
cat("\nAFT系数:\n")
## 
## AFT系数:
print(beta_aft_weibull)
## (Intercept)         sex         age 
##  6.27485306  0.38208514 -0.01225703
# 转换为PH系数
beta_ph_weibull <- -beta_aft_weibull / scale
cat("\nPH系数:\n")
## 
## PH系数:
print(beta_ph_weibull[-1])
##        sex        age 
## -0.5067100  0.0162549

检验Weibull假设

# 绘制log(H(t)) vs log(t)
# 如果是Weibull分布，应该是直线，斜率为alpha

km_fit <- survfit(Surv(time, status - 1) ~ 1, data = lung_clean)

# 计算累积风险
cumhaz <- -log(km_fit$surv)

# 去除0值
valid_idx <- cumhaz > 0 & km_fit$time > 0

plot(log(km_fit$time[valid_idx]), log(cumhaz[valid_idx]),
     xlab = "log(Time)", ylab = "log(Cumulative Hazard)",
     main = "Check Weibull Assumption",
     pch = 19, col = "blue")

# 拟合直线
fit_line <- lm(log(cumhaz[valid_idx]) ~ log(km_fit$time[valid_idx]))
abline(fit_line, col = "red", lwd = 2)

cat("如果点近似直线，则支持Weibull分布\n")
## 如果点近似直线，则支持Weibull分布
cat("斜率估计:", coef(fit_line)[2], "\n")
## 斜率估计: 1.223005

# Log-normal模型
lognorm_model <- survreg(Surv(time, status - 1) ~ sex + age,
                         data = lung_clean, dist = "lognormal")

# Log-logistic模型
loglogistic_model <- survreg(Surv(time, status - 1) ~ sex + age,
                              data = lung_clean, dist = "loglogistic")

# 比较所有模型的AIC
model_comparison <- data.frame(
  Distribution = c("Exponential", "Weibull", "Log-normal", "Log-logistic"),
  AIC = c(AIC(exp_model), AIC(weibull_model),
          AIC(lognorm_model), AIC(loglogistic_model)),
  LogLik = c(logLik(exp_model), logLik(weibull_model),
             logLik(lognorm_model), logLik(loglogistic_model))
)

print(model_comparison)
##   Distribution      AIC    LogLik
## 1  Exponential 2318.198 -1156.099
## 2      Weibull 2302.109 -1147.054
## 3   Log-normal 2325.500 -1158.750
## 4 Log-logistic 2313.794 -1152.897
cat("\n最佳模型（最小AIC）:",
    model_comparison$Distribution[which.min(model_comparison$AIC)], "\n")

## 最佳模型（最小AIC）: Weibull

# 创建时间依赖协变量的简单示例
# 假设治疗状态在时间50改变

set.seed(456)
n <- 50
base_time <- rexp(n, 0.02)
censor_time <- runif(n, 0, 150)

# 观测时间和事件指示
obs_time <- pmin(base_time, censor_time)
event_indicator <- as.numeric(base_time < censor_time)

# 创建时间段数据
# 每个个体最多有两行：0-50和50-结束
tdc_list <- list()
for(i in 1:n) {
  if(obs_time[i] <= 50) {
    # 如果在50之前就结束，只有一行
    tdc_list[[i]] <- data.frame(
      id = i,
      start = 0,
      stop = obs_time[i],
      event = event_indicator[i],
      trt = 0,
      age = rnorm(1, 60, 10)
    )
  } else {
    # 如果存活超过50，有两行
    tdc_list[[i]] <- data.frame(
      id = c(i, i),
      start = c(0, 50),
      stop = c(50, obs_time[i]),
      event = c(0, event_indicator[i]),
      trt = c(0, 1),  # 治疗在时间50开始
      age = rep(rnorm(1, 60, 10), 2)
    )
  }
}

tdc_data <- do.call(rbind, tdc_list)

9.2 HR解释

# HR解释示例
beta <- 0.5
hr <- exp(beta)

cat("=== 风险比(HR)解释 ===\n\n")
## === 风险比(HR)解释 ===
cat("系数 beta =", beta, "\n")
## 系数 beta = 0.5
cat("HR = exp(beta) =", hr, "\n\n")
## HR = exp(beta) = 1.648721
cat("正确解释:\n")
## 正确解释:
cat("✓ '暴露组的风险是对照组的", hr, "倍'\n")
## ✓ '暴露组的风险是对照组的 1.648721 倍'
cat("✓ '暴露组的风险比对照组增加", (hr - 1) * 100, "%'\n")
## ✓ '暴露组的风险比对照组增加 64.87213 %'
cat("✓ '暴露增加了", (hr - 1) * 100, "%的风险'\n\n")
## ✓ '暴露增加了 64.87213 %的风险'
cat("错误解释:\n")
## 错误解释:
cat("✗ '暴露组的生存概率是对照组的", hr, "倍'\n")
## ✗ '暴露组的生存概率是对照组的 1.648721 倍'
cat("✗ '风险降低", (1 - hr) * 100, "%'（当HR>1时）\n\n")
## ✗ '风险降低 -64.87213 %'（当HR>1时）
# HR < 1的情况
beta_neg <- -0.5
hr_neg <- exp(beta_neg)

cat("当 beta =", beta_neg, ", HR =", hr_neg, ":\n")
## 当 beta = -0.5 , HR = 0.6065307 :
cat("✓ '保护因素，风险降低", (1 - hr_neg) * 100, "%'\n")
## ✓ '保护因素，风险降低 39.34693 %'
cat("✓ '风险是对照组的", hr_neg, "倍'\n")
## ✓ '风险是对照组的 0.6065307 倍'

9.3 调整前后HR变化

# 示例：混杂的影响
set.seed(999)
n <- 500

# 生成数据，age是混杂因素
age <- rnorm(n, 60, 10)
treatment <- rbinom(n, 1, plogis((age - 60) / 10))  # 治疗与年龄相关
time <- rexp(n, exp(-0.5 * treatment + 0.03 * age))
event <- rbinom(n, 1, 0.7)

conf_data <- data.frame(time, event, treatment, age)

# 未调整模型
cox_unadj <- coxph(Surv(time, event) ~ treatment, data = conf_data)

# 调整模型
cox_adj <- coxph(Surv(time, event) ~ treatment + age, data = conf_data)

cat("=== 混杂效应示例 ===\n\n")
## === 混杂效应示例 ===
cat("未调整HR (treatment):\n")
## 未调整HR (treatment):
cat("  HR =", round(exp(coef(cox_unadj)), 3), "\n")
##   HR = 0.831
cat("  95% CI:", paste(round(exp(confint(cox_unadj)), 3), collapse = ", "), "\n\n")
##   95% CI: 0.672, 1.027
cat("调整年龄后HR (treatment):\n")
## 调整年龄后HR (treatment):
cat("  HR =", round(exp(coef(cox_adj)["treatment"]), 3), "\n")
##   HR = 0.693
cat("  95% CI:", paste(round(exp(confint(cox_adj)["treatment", ]), 3), collapse = ", "), "\n\n")
##   95% CI: 0.548, 0.877
change_pct <- (exp(coef(cox_adj)["treatment"]) - exp(coef(cox_unadj))) /
               exp(coef(cox_unadj)) * 100

cat("HR变化:", round(change_pct, 1), "%\n")
## HR变化: -16.6 %
if(abs(change_pct) > 10) {
  cat("变化>10%，提示存在混杂\n")
}
## 变化>10%，提示存在混杂

总结和考试提示

关键公式速查

关键公式总结
Topic Formula
Survival Function S(t) = P(T > t) = exp(-H(t))
Hazard Function h(t) = f(t)/S(t) = -d log S(t)/dt
Cumulative Hazard H(t) = ∫ h(u)du = -log S(t)
Relationship 1 h(t) = f(t)/S(t)
Relationship 2 S(t) = exp(-∫ h(u)du)
KM Estimator Ŝ(t) = ∏(1 - d_i/r_i)
Greenwood Variance Var(Ŝ) = Ŝ²∑[d_i/(r_i(r_i-d_i))]
Logrank Statistic χ² = (O₁-E₁)²/V
Cox Model h(t|Z) = h₀(t)exp(β’Z)
Hazard Ratio HR = exp(β)
Backward Calculation d_i/r_i = 1 - Ŝ(t_i)/Ŝ(t_{i-1})

考试检查清单

计算题检查点

  1. KM估计
    • ✓ 风险集r_i的计算正确（包括当前时间点的事件，不包括删失）
    • ✓ 逐步计算每个时间点的生存概率
    • ✓ Greenwood方差只在事件时间求和
    • ✓ 最终结果在[0,1]区间
  2. Logrank检验
    • ✓ 每个事件时间都计算E_i和V_i
    • ✓ 合并两组数据找所有事件时间
    • ✓ 检验统计量=(O-E)²/V
    • ✓ 自由度=组数-1
  3. Cox模型解释
    • ✓ β>0 → HR>1 → 风险增加
    • ✓ β<0 → HR<1 → 风险降低
    • ✓ 说明参考组
    • ✓ 连续变量说明单位（每增加1单位/10单位）
    • ✓ CI不包含1则显著
  4. Backward Calculation
    • ✓ 使用d_i/r_i = 1 - Ŝ(t_i)/Ŝ(t_{i-1})
    • ✓ 追踪r_{i+1} = r_i - d_i - c_i
    • ✓ 检查∑d_i + ∑c_i = n

概念题要点

关键概念总结
Topic Key_Points
删失类型 右删失最常见；左截断≠左删失；非信息删失是关键假设
PH假设 HR不随时间变化；log-log图平行；Schoenfeld检验
混杂 >10%HR变化提示混杂；调整后HR更准确
交互作用 一个变量的效应取决于另一个变量；检验交互项系数
分层 不同基线风险但相同β；用于PH假设违反
模型选择 AIC越小越好；LR检验比较嵌套模型；平衡拟合和复杂度
